WEBVTT

00:06.527 --> 00:08.293
<i>Previously on</i>
<i>Masters Of Sex...</i>

00:08.329 --> 00:09.762
Dan: The thought
of not seeing you every day

00:09.797 --> 00:11.797
is not something
I'm ready to accept just now.

00:11.832 --> 00:13.165
Virginia: And your wife?

00:13.200 --> 00:14.833
Dan: My wife and I have
an understanding.

00:14.869 --> 00:16.769
So, what if
I keep coming here...

00:16.804 --> 00:18.837
because we love each other?

00:18.873 --> 00:20.439
Paul:
What are you doing here, Libby?

00:20.474 --> 00:22.975
Libby: I am so sick
of pretending all the time.

00:23.010 --> 00:24.610
Paul:
I want you to be my wife.

00:24.645 --> 00:26.178
Libby: [ Crying ]

00:26.230 --> 00:27.346
Johnny:
Dennis went to my dad--

00:27.398 --> 00:29.515
and my dad had to show Dennis

00:29.517 --> 00:32.183
a book on how to fix
his broken penis.

00:32.186 --> 00:34.820
William: It's incredibly common
and perfectly normal.

00:35.322 --> 00:37.439
Dennis: - Ow!
William: - John!

00:37.491 --> 00:40.292
Virginia: In two weeks, Bill and
I are going into Little Brown

00:40.327 --> 00:42.995
to present the initial research
for our second book.

00:43.030 --> 00:44.797
If he finds out about us,

00:44.832 --> 00:46.365
he might even keep me
out of the work,

00:46.367 --> 00:48.117
which he's done before.

00:48.169 --> 00:49.735
Lester: All these women
either want to marry me

00:49.770 --> 00:51.203
or they look at me
like I'm some sort of torturer.

00:51.205 --> 00:52.788
Virginia: This is what I've been
saying all along.

00:52.840 --> 00:54.840
This program doesn't work!

00:54.875 --> 00:57.042
William: Look, if-- if you're not
comfortable with the surrogacy work,

00:57.044 --> 00:58.577
then... we can't continue.

00:58.612 --> 01:00.546
I just want it to be us again...

01:00.548 --> 01:01.964
together.

01:02.016 --> 01:03.215
Virginia:
That's what I want, too.

01:03.267 --> 01:04.849
Betty: I think the doc

01:04.885 --> 01:08.020
is a little worried
about Mr. Logan's presence.

01:08.055 --> 01:09.655
Virginia:
So, Bill sent you to...

01:09.690 --> 01:11.090
pump me for information?

01:11.125 --> 01:12.691
Betty: Maybe I can spare you
a lot of grief

01:12.727 --> 01:14.827
by sharing with you a tidbit
I have picked up--

01:14.862 --> 01:19.231
Trying to control other people
doesn't work, ever.

01:19.233 --> 01:23.736
The only person you can control
is yourself.

